claim.claim-text:
18. A wafer clamping mechanism, comprising: 
a robot arm; 
a wrist located near the distal end of said robotic arm; 
a wafer carrying blade coupled to said wrist; and 
at least two four-bar linkage mechanisms coupled to said wrist, said four-bar linkage mechanisms automatically clamping a wafer onto said blade when said robotic arm is in its retracted position.
